          <mainBody>
            <p><span style="color:#0070C0"><b>Annex A - Territorial extent and application in the United Kingdom</b></span></p>
            <blockContainer>
              <num>31 </num>
              <p><span style="color:#000000">The Act extends to England and Wales but applies in England only, save for the consequential amendments to other enactments, which have the same extent as the provisions being amended.</span></p>
            </blockContainer>
          </mainBody>
        </doc>
